window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Victory of any kind is a victory. Nick and Neako are back onboard with their team and ready to crack heads.<br> <br> After shooting their way through the armada of alien ships, they find themselves in a large, bleak galaxy filled with a variety of life.<br> <br> But they arenâ€™t looking to fit in. They are looking for <i>Retribution</i>.<br> <br> Follow Nick and his team as they blast their way to the top of the food chain, one dead Tiokien at a time.<br> <br> This is a LitRPG book with game system-levels, stats, and cool abilities. No Harem and loads of fun violence.</p>"; 
